<div class="block">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="block__content split">
      <h2 class="h2">The two Manchester Homelessness Partnership awards are:</h2>
      <div class="split__element">
        <h3 class="h3">Commended Best Practice</h3>
        <p>To be eligible to receive the award for Commended Best Practice, your organisation must have:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>An organisation bank account</li>
          <li>Public Liability Insurance</li>
          <li>Policies in place:</li>
          <li>Safeguarding</li>
          <li>Confidentiality</li>
          <li>Health and Safety</li>
          <li>Financial Policy</li>
        </ul>
        <p>A group leader with a current <a href="https://www.gov.uk/disclosure-barring-service-check/overview">DBS (Disclosure and Barring Service)</a>.</p>

      </div>
      <div class="split__element">
        <h3 class="h3">Distinctive Best Practice</h3>
        <p>To receive the award for Distinctive Best Practice, your organisation must have:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>All Commended Best Practice conditions in place.</li>
          <li>A volunteer induction process, including application form, reference and identification checks</li>
          <li>Lone working policy</li>
          <li>Volunteer policy</li>
          <li>Blood borne diseases policy</li>
          <li>Social media usage policy</li>
          <li>Data protection policy</li>
          <li>A reliable and responsible service</li>
          <li>A DBS checked volunteer present at all times</li>
        <ul>
      </div>
    </div>
